    "text": "我們使用 Kaggle 50 Startups 資料集，分析研發、行政、行銷與地區，對公司利潤的影響。",
    "media": "assets/edge_yunjhe_segments/segment_02.mp3",
    "subtitles": "assets/edge_yunjhe_segments/segment_02.vtt"
  },
  {
    "index": 3,
    "voice": "zh-TW-YunJheNeural",
    "rate": "+8%",
    "pitch": "+0Hz",
    "text": "整個流程採用 CRISP-DM，從商業理解，到資料理解、資料準備、建模、評估，最後走向部署。",
    "media": "assets/edge_yunjhe_segments/segment_03.mp3",
    "subtitles": "assets/edge_yunjhe_segments/segment_03.vtt"
  },
  {
    "index": 4,
    "voice": "zh-TW-YunJheNeural",
    "rate": "+8%",
    "pitch": "+0Hz",
    "text": "在商業目標上，我們不只想預測利潤，也想知道哪些支出真正推動成長。",
    "media": "assets/edge_yunjhe_segments/segment_04.mp3",
    "subtitles": "assets/edge_yunjhe_segments/segment_04.vtt"
  },
  {
    "index": 5,
    "voice": "zh-TW-YunJheNeural",
    "rate": "+8%",
    "pitch": "+0Hz",
    "text": "資料集共有五十筆新創公司資料，欄位包含 R and D spend、Administration、Marketing Spend、State，以及 Profit。",
    "media": "assets/edge_yunjhe_segments/segment_05.mp3",
    "subtitles": "assets/edge_yunjhe_segments/segment_05.vtt"
  },
  {
    "index": 6,
    "voice": "zh-TW-YunJheNeural",
    "rate": "+8%",
    "pitch": "+0Hz",
    "text": "初步探索顯示，利潤分布相當接近常態，州別樣本也相對平衡，因此資料本身適合進一步建模。",
    "media": "assets/edge_yunjhe_segments/segment_06.mp3",
    "subtitles": "assets/edge_yunjhe_segments/segment_06.vtt"
  },
  {
    "index": 7,
    "voice": "zh-TW-YunJheNeural",
    "rate": "+8%",
    "pitch": "+0Hz",
    "text": "相關矩陣揭露最重要的訊號：研發支出與利潤的相關係數高達零點九七三，是最強的線性關係。",
    "media": "assets/edge_yunjhe_segments/segment_07.mp3",
    "subtitles": "assets/edge_yunjhe_segments/segment_07.vtt"
  },
  {
    "index": 8,
    "voice": "zh-TW-YunJheNeural",
    "rate": "+8%",
    "pitch": "+0Hz",
    "text": "同時，行銷支出也有正向關聯；但行政支出與地區變數，對利潤的直接解釋力明顯較弱。",
    "media": "assets/edge_yunjhe_segments/segment_08.mp3",
    "subtitles": "assets/edge_yunjhe_segments/segment_08.vtt"
  },
  {
    "index": 9,
    "voice": "zh-TW-YunJheNeural",
    "rate": "+8%",
    "pitch": "+0Hz",
    "text": "在資料準備階段，我們保留有效離群值，因為它代表真實商業失敗案例，而不是單純錯誤資料。",
