    "subtitles": "assets/edge_yunjhe_segments/segment_09.vtt"
  },
  {
    "index": 10,
    "voice": "zh-TW-YunJheNeural",
    "rate": "+8%",
    "pitch": "+0Hz",
    "text": "類別變數透過 One Hot Encoding 轉換，數值欄位則使用 StandardScaler，避免尺度差異影響模型。",
    "media": "assets/edge_yunjhe_segments/segment_10.mp3",
    "subtitles": "assets/edge_yunjhe_segments/segment_10.vtt"
  },
  {
    "index": 11,
    "voice": "zh-TW-YunJheNeural",
    "rate": "+8%",
    "pitch": "+0Hz",
    "text": "建模階段比較三種方法：Multiple Linear Regression、Ridge Regression，以及 Random Forest Regressor。",
