    "voice": "zh-TW-YunJheNeural",
    "rate": "+8%",
    "pitch": "+0Hz",
    "text": "測試集結果顯示，Random Forest 的 R squared 達到零點九一四七，MAE 與 RMSE 也最低。",
    "media": "assets/edge_yunjhe_segments/segment_12.mp3",
    "subtitles": "assets/edge_yunjhe_segments/segment_12.vtt"
  },
  {
    "index": 13,
    "voice": "zh-TW-YunJheNeural",
    "rate": "+8%",
    "pitch": "+0Hz",
    "text": "不過交叉驗證告訴我們，線性模型其實非常穩定，代表這個資料集的主要結構仍然偏線性。",
